{
  "stem": "18670.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 225.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Basically, I-- I was the one that pushed that we should get out of Austria, that there isn't any future in Austria, because I believed what I read.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believed in Hitler's",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1938, I was 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't 19 yet when Hitler marched in, but I was 19 in June of the same year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to Vienna several times to see whether we could get a visa to one of the countries.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I realized-- I came back and told my parents it's impossible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody wants the Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- even though I said we're going to get affidavits and I know there will be work done in America, nobody wanted Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were endless lines in front of every embassy in Vienna and there wasn't an opening to go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There just wasn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came back and I says there isn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I have heard that there's such a thing as leaving Austria illegally and go to another country.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I sat down with a map and I says, here, the German side, there are all these borders.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only way I feel we could escape is through Germany, because nobody is going to stop us there, going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And went back to Vienna and I found people that had set up call it railroad, whatever it was, where you left Vienna and you went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You went to Cologne, Germany, and from Cologne, to Aachen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Aachen, you had three borders there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So if you couldn't get into one country, you could get into another one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time, I only had-- one side you had Luxembourg and France.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the other one, you had Belgium, then you had Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
